Store Assistant (1 year Contract) (ANALYTICAL/201308/01/SG)
Job ID
EPM-00005229
Country
Singapore
State/Province
Singapore
City
Singapore
Publish Start Date
Aug 25 2013
Job Level
Non-Professional (Will not auto post to LinkedIn)
|
Responsibilities:
Receive and check goods to ensure that incoming shipment match the purchase orders.
Coordinate with vendors for the schedule of delivery and escalate any discrepancy in quantity and quality to Project/QA Engineer.
Maintain an accurate project inventory list.
Ensure proper documentation, storage of goods and maintenance of project store in accordance to required safety standards.
Support project team by arranging for fabrication area, transferring materials to contractors for fabrication and assembly purpose as well as in packing of projects.
Assist in all export pre-shipment and shipment arrangements.
Requirements:
ITC/NTC with minimum 1 year experience in store management.
Knowledge in JDE/Oracle/SAP.
Forklift skill/license.